Start off
  git clone [link to repo here]


commiting steps
1)
    git add .
 or git rm --cached filename
2)
    git commit -m "comments"
3)
    git push

Branching Steps
git branch newBranchName
git checkout branchName

git branch -d experiment // delete experiment, after it already been merged
git branch -D experiment // force delete experiment, without merging it

